'''Peter Flügel''' is an Indologist who has many publications related to Indian religions and history to his credit.<ref>{{citation |title=Peter Flügel |url=https://www.soas.ac.uk/staff/staff30946.php |work=SOAS, University of London }}</ref><ref>{{citation |title=Lectures by Dr Peter Flugel |url=http://www.ochs.org.uk/lectures/by-name-sorter/Dr%20Peter%20Flugel |work=THE OXFORD CENTRE FOR HINDU STUDIES }}</ref> He is a scholar of Jainism at the School of Oriental and African Studies at the University of London.<ref>{{citation |title=A Jain library steps gingerly into the 21st century |url=http://gazette.com/a-jain-library-steps-gingerly-into-the-21st-century/article/1602791 |work=[[The Gazette (Colorado Springs)|The Gazette]] |date=9 May 2017 }}</ref>

He serves as principal investigator for two papers, [https://www.soas.ac.uk/jainastudies/research/aniconic-jaina-tradition/ Literary Heritage of the Aniconic Jaina Tradition]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.soas.ac.uk/jainastudies/research/aniconic-jaina-tradition/|title=Literary Heritage of the Aniconic Jaina Tradition, Centre of Jaina Studies, SOAS University of London|website=www.soas.ac.uk|language=en|access-date=2018-10-28}}</ref>, and [https://www.soas.ac.uk/jaina-prosopography/ Jaina-Prosopography: Monastic Lineages, Networks and Patronage]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.soas.ac.uk/jaina-prosopography/|title=Jaina-Prosopography: Monastic Lineages, Networks and Patronage {{!}} SOAS University of London|website=www.soas.ac.uk|language=en|access-date=2018-10-28}}</ref>

'''Peter Flügel''' chairs the [https://www.soas.ac.uk/jainastudies/ Center of Jaina Studies]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.soas.ac.uk/jainastudies/|title=Centre of Jaina Studies at SOAS, University of London|website=www.soas.ac.uk|language=en|access-date=2018-10-28}}</ref>, and is a member of the [https://www.soas.ac.uk/buddhiststudies/ Center of Buddhist Studies]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.soas.ac.uk/buddhiststudies/|title=Centre of Buddhist Studies at SOAS University of London|website=www.soas.ac.uk|language=en|access-date=2018-10-28}}</ref>




